      "title": "Track upstream wait --download saveAs persistence bug",
      "description": "agent-browser 0.26.0 reports success for wait --download <path> with data.path/savedFilePath equal to the requested path, but in this environment the requested file is not created; the browser writes the fixture download to the default Downloads directory instead. Track or report the upstream saveAs/persistence issue, then update the real-upstream contract and docs once upstream reliably persists the requested path.",
